msgid "# Qwen3-ASR-1.7B"
msgstr "# Qwen3-ASR-1.7B"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 引言"

msgid ""
"Qwen3-ASR-1.7B is a 1.7B-parameter automatic speech recognition (ASR) model "
"from the Qwen team. It supports Chinese and English speech, Chinese "
"dialects, multilingual speech, and singing voice transcription, and provides"
" long-audio and streaming inference capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-ASR-1.7B 是 Qwen 团队推出的 1.7B "
"参数自动语音识别（ASR）模型。它支持中英文语音、中文方言、多语种语音及歌声转录，并提供长音频和流式推理能力。"

msgid ""
"This document describes the supported features, environment preparation, "
"single-node deployment, functional verification, and evaluation workflow for"
" Qwen3-ASR-1.7B on Ascend NPUs."
msgstr "本文档描述了 Qwen3-ASR-1.7B 在昇腾 NPU 上支持的特性、环境准备、单节点部署、功能验证及评估流程。"

msgid ""
"Qwen3-ASR-1.7B was introduced with upstream vLLM v0.19.0. Use a vLLM-Ascend "
"image that matches your vLLM version, and refer to the support matrix for "
"the current release status."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-ASR-1.7B 随上游 vLLM v0.19.0 版本引入。请使用与 vLLM 版本匹配的 vLLM-Ascend "
"镜像，并参考支持矩阵了解当前发布状态。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Please refer to the [Supported Features "
"List](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) for the model "
"support matrix."
msgstr ""
"模型支持矩阵请参考[支持特性列表](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)。"

msgid ""
"Please refer to the [Feature Guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)"
" for feature configuration information."
msgstr "特性配置信息请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)。"

msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"The BF16 model can be deployed with one Ascend 910B 64 GB NPU or one Ascend "
"Atlas inference products 48 GB NPU. Download the model weights from "
"[ModelScope](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B)."
msgstr ""
"BF16 模型可使用单张昇腾 910B 64 GB NPU 或单张昇腾 Atlas 推理产品 48 GB NPU 进行部署。请从 "
"[ModelScope](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B) 下载模型权重。"

msgid ""
"Download the weights to a directory that is accessible from the deployment "
"environment. For multi-node deployments, use a shared directory; for "
"example, `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "将权重下载到部署环境可访问的目录。对于多节点部署，请使用共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

msgid ""
"Use the vLLM-Ascend Docker image that corresponds to your hardware. Replace "
"the model-weight mount with the path used in your environment."
msgstr "使用与硬件对应的 vLLM-Ascend Docker 镜像。请将模型权重挂载路径替换为您环境中的实际路径。"

msgid "=== \"Atlas A2 inference products\""
msgstr "=== \"Atlas A2 推理产品\""

msgid "=== \"Atlas inference products\""
msgstr "=== \"Atlas 推理产品\""

msgid ""
"Verify that the container is running and that the installed package version "
"matches the image tag:"
msgstr "验证容器正在运行，并且已安装的包版本与镜像标签匹配："

msgid ""
"Expected result: `docker ps` lists the container with status `Up`, and `pip "
"show` displays version information for both packages."
msgstr "预期结果：`docker ps` 列出状态为 `Up` 的容器，`pip show` 显示两个包的版本信息。"

msgid "### 4.2 Source Code Installation"
msgstr "### 4.2 源码安装"

msgid ""
"f you prefer to build from source instead of using the Docker image, install"
" vLLM-Ascend following the [Installation Guide](../../installation.md)."
msgstr ""
"如果您希望从源码构建而非使用 Docker 镜像，请按照[安装指南](../../installation.md)安装 vLLM-Ascend。"

msgid ""
"For Atlas inference products, source installation may pull in `triton` and "
"`triton-ascend`. Uninstall them before running vLLM-Ascend on Atlas "
"inference products:"
msgstr ""
"对于 Atlas 推理产品，源码安装可能会引入 `triton` 和 `triton-ascend`。在 Atlas 推理产品上运行 vLLM-"
"Ascend 之前，请先卸载它们："

msgid "To verify the source installation:"
msgstr "验证源码安装："

msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment runs both audio prefill and decoding on one NPU, "
"making it suitable for development, testing, and small-scale ASR services. "
"Replace `your_model_path` with the local model directory, or use "
"`Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B` to download the model through the configured model "
"hub."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在单张 NPU 上同时运行音频预填充和解码，适用于开发、测试及小规模 ASR 服务。请将 `your_model_path` "
"替换为本地模型目录，或使用 `Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B` 通过配置的模型仓库下载模型。"

msgid ""
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 1` uses one NPU. Increase it only after confirming that the hardware and deployment topology support the chosen parallel configuration.\n"
"        - `--max-model-len 4096` limits the maximum sequence length. On Atlas 300I DUO, always specify a conservative value explicitly; automatic detection can allocate an oversized attention mask and cause an out-of-memory error.\n"
"        - `--gpu-memory-utilization 0.9` sets the fraction of device memory available to the vLLM executor. Lower this value if other workloads share the NPU.\n"
"        - `--enforce-eager` disables graph execution. It is used in the Atlas 300I A2 2UP example for compatibility."
msgstr ""
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 1` 使用单张 NPU。仅在确认硬件和部署拓扑支持所选并行配置后，再增加此值。\n"
"        - `--max-model-len 4096` 限制最大序列长度。在 Atlas 300I DUO 上，务必显式指定一个保守值；自动检测可能会分配过大的注意力掩码，导致内存不足错误。\n"
"        - `--gpu-memory-utilization 0.9` 设置 vLLM 执行器可用的设备内存比例。如果其他工作负载共享 NPU，请降低此值。\n"
"        - `--enforce-eager` 禁用图执行。在 Atlas 300I A2 2UP 示例中用于兼容性。"

msgid ""
"When the service starts successfully, the log contains `Application startup "
"complete`. If startup fails, see the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)."
msgstr ""
"当服务成功启动时，日志中包含 `Application startup complete`。如果启动失败，请参阅[公共 "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)。"

msgid "## 6 Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 6 功能验证"

msgid ""
"After the service is started, the model can be invoked by sending a prompt."
msgstr "服务启动后，可通过发送提示词来调用模型。"

msgid "**Chat Completions API:**"
msgstr "**聊天补全 API：**"

msgid ""
"Replace `localhost`, `8000`, and `qwen3-asr` with the address, port, and "
"`--served-model-name` used by your deployment. Expected result: HTTP 200 and"
" a JSON response containing the transcription in the `choices` field."
msgstr ""
"将 `localhost`、`8000` 和 `qwen3-asr` 替换为部署中使用的地址、端口和 `--served-model-"
"name`。预期结果：HTTP 200 以及一个 JSON 响应，其中 `choices` 字段包含转录文本。"

msgid "## 7 Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 7 精度评估"

msgid ""
"Evaluate transcription quality with Word Error Rate (WER) for word-level "
"recognition and Character Error Rate (CER) for character-level recognition."
msgstr "使用词错误率（WER）评估词级识别质量，使用字符错误率（CER）评估字符级识别质量。"

msgid "## 8 Performance Evaluation"
msgstr "## 8 性能评估"

msgid ""
"Measure ASR serving performance with audio samples that represent the "
"production workload. Record at least the audio duration, request "
"concurrency, end-to-end latency, real-time factor, and throughput. This "
"ensures that audio preprocessing, request construction, API communication, "
"inference, and response parsing are included in the result."
msgstr ""
"使用代表生产工作负载的音频样本来测量 ASR 服务性能。至少记录音频时长、请求并发数、端到端延迟、实时因子和吞吐量。这确保音频预处理、请求构建、API "
"通信、推理和响应解析都包含在结果中。"

msgid ""
"Actual performance varies with hardware, audio duration, concurrency, and "
"deployment configuration. Evaluate short audio, long audio, and concurrent "
"requests separately before selecting a production configuration."
msgstr "实际性能因硬件、音频时长、并发数和部署配置而异。在选择生产配置之前，请分别评估短音频、长音频和并发请求。"

msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid ""
"The following settings are starting points rather than globally optimal "
"configurations. Tune them according to audio duration, concurrency, latency "
"requirements, and available NPU memory."
msgstr "以下设置是起点而非全局最优配置。请根据音频时长、并发数、延迟要求和可用 NPU 内存进行调整。"

msgid "| Scenario | Recommended Starting Point | Key Considerations |"
msgstr "| 场景 | 推荐起点 | 关键考量 |"

msgid ""
"| Low latency | `--tensor-parallel-size 1`, `--max-model-len 4096` | Use "
"short audio inputs and avoid sharing the NPU with other workloads. |"
msgstr ""
"| 低延迟 | `--tensor-parallel-size 1`, `--max-model-len 4096` | "
"使用短音频输入，避免与其他工作负载共享 NPU。 |"

msgid ""
"| High throughput | Increase request concurrency after establishing the "
"latency baseline | Monitor NPU memory and end-to-end latency; do not use "
"synthetic text-only requests as a proxy for ASR traffic. |"
msgstr "| 高吞吐量 | 建立延迟基线后增加请求并发数 | 监控 NPU 内存和端到端延迟；不要使用合成的纯文本请求来模拟 ASR 流量。 |"

msgid ""
"| Long audio | Increase `--max-model-len` only as required | On Atlas "
"inference products, keep the value conservative because attention-mask "
"memory grows with the configured maximum length. |"
msgstr ""
"| 长音频 | 仅在必要时增加 `--max-model-len` | "
"在Atlas推理产品上，请保守设置该值，因为注意力掩码内存会随配置的最大长度增长。 |"

msgid ""
"For general parameter tuning, refer to the [Performance Tuning "
"Guide](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关通用参数调优，请参考[性能调优指南](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)。"

msgid "## 10 FAQ"
msgstr "## 10 常见问题"

msgid ""
"For common environment, installation, and general parameter issues, see the "
"[Public FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html). This"
" section covers model- and hardware-specific guidance."
msgstr ""
"关于常见环境、安装和通用参数问题，请参阅[公共常见问题](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)。本节涵盖模型和硬件相关的指导。"

msgid "### Atlas inference products runs out of memory during startup"
msgstr "### Atlas推理产品在启动时内存不足"

msgid ""
"**Symptom:** The server fails with an out-of-memory error while initializing"
" attention."
msgstr "**症状：** 服务器在初始化注意力机制时因内存不足错误而失败。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** On Atlas inference products, an automatically detected large "
"context length can create a full causal attention mask whose memory "
"consumption grows quadratically with `max_model_len`."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** 在Atlas推理产品上，自动检测到的较大上下文长度可能会生成完整的因果注意力掩码，其内存消耗随 `max_model_len` "
"呈二次方增长。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Always set `--max-model-len` explicitly to a conservative "
"value, such as `4096`, and increase it only after verifying available NPU "
"memory."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 始终显式地将 `--max-model-len` 设置为保守值（例如 `4096`），并在确认NPU内存可用后再增加该值。"
